name: GUNSHO's DEMONOLOGY- BAEL
description: GUNSHO’s DEMONOLOGY- BAEL 18×24 inch 5-color screen print on 140lb white. Stamped and numbered edition of 150. The Goetia, or The Lesser Key of Solomon the King, is a handbook of astrological sorcery that gives detailed instructions for summoning and seeking the aid of its 72 demons. GUNSHO’s Demonology is an intensive effort to recreate the 72 demons of the Goetia and other works of demonology. Each demon will be the subject of a print.
